  "text": "Scholarship notes that learning may also provide important knowledge related to marketing, new product development and R&D, thus facilitating internationalisation activities [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Due to its key role, prior research suggests that learning facilitates the development and evolution of capabilities in INVs [CITATION_3] .",
